We can see that the sets (A △ B) × A, (A × B) △ A, and (B × A) △ B are all different:

(A △ B) × A = {(1,1), (1,2), (1,3), (2,1), (2,2), (2,3), (4,1), (4,2), (4,3), (5,1), (5,2), (5,3)}

